For those of you still struggling with this - Rename the .001 to .016 files to .r01 to .r16 - then use Winrar to extract the bin and cue files - Then mount the cue file useing Virtual Daemon Manager (search in google) and run the install - very easy really - thanks to torsk for an excellent job.
